U-Click is Kensence(shenzhen)Technology Development CO.,Ltd developed a mirror software that between smart terminals,it is a high performance projection screen tool, is committed to creating a projection screen platform between intelligent terminals. The software uses the projection screens patent technology to realize the interactive mirror between different intelligent terminals, and provides a unique and fast channel for video information exchange between handheld end users. Android system equipment and Windows system equipment which installed U-Click software can realize the interactive mirror . At the same time , Android system equipment and Windows system equipment can mirror the screen to the iOS system and Mac OS system equipment; iOS system equipment, Mac OS system equipment also can mirror the screen to the projection screen device through the AirPlay protocol. In addition, U-Click has a unique feature, you can mirror the screen of Android system and Windows system equipment in the form of broadcast to the Android system equipment, Windows system equipment, iOS system equipment, Mac OS system equipment at the same time. The realization of this technology,added a variety of face-to-face timely interactive function for the handheld terminal , will greatly meet the intelligent end-user pursuit of high, new, odd nature, become our favorite new hot spots.
